”巡演。</p><p>去年五月，海姆斯沃斯回顾了公众对他的健康更新的反应， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/chris-hemsworth-response-alzheimers-reveval-pissed-me-off-3752433">他毫不讳言</a>。</p><p> “这真的让我很生气，因为我感觉自己在一些私人的事情上很脆弱，并分享了这些，”他说。 “无论我怎么说‘这不是死刑’，故事都变成了我患有痴呆症，我正在重新考虑生活和退休等等。”</p><p>海姆斯沃斯随后回忆起在网上看到一条与他的倾向相关的诙谐评论：“我确实在一篇文章的底部读到了一条非常有趣的评论：‘我希望克里斯忘记他要退休了，然后回来。’”当月晚些时候，海姆斯沃斯<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/robert-downey-jr-roasts-chris-hemsworth-during-hollywood-walk-of-fame-star-unveiling-3759257">收到了好莱坞星光大道上有他自己的星星</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/chris-hemsworth-makes-surprise-appearance-as-drummer-at-ed-sheeran-show-in-romania-3786878">克里斯·海姆斯沃斯 (Chris Hemsworth) 在罗马尼亚埃德·希兰 (Ed Sheeran) 演出中作为鼓手出人意料地亮相，</a>这一消息首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
由于阿联酋卷入“灾难性”苏丹危机，麦克莫尔取消迪拜展会https://www.nme.com/news/music/macklemore-cancels-dubai-show-ongoing-sudan-crisis-3786864?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=macklemore-cancels-dubai-show-ongoing-sudan-crisisDaniel Peters Sun, 25 Aug 2024 09:19:09 +0000 Music NewsNewsRap https://www.nme.com/?p=3786864 <p><img width="1392" height="884" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Macklemore-2024-Getty.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="麦克莫尔迪拜" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Macklemore-2024-Getty.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Macklemore-2024-Getty-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Macklemore-2024-Getty-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Macklemore-2024-Getty-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Macklemore-2024-Getty-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 1392px) 100vw, 1392px" /></p><p> “我不想出于恐惧而做出决定，而是发自内心的慎重决定”</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/macklemore-cancels-dubai-show-ongoing-sudan-crisis-3786864">由于阿联酋卷入“灾难性”苏丹危机，麦克勒莫尔取消迪拜展会的</a>消息首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="1392" height="884" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Macklemore-2024-Getty.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="麦克莫尔迪拜" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Macklemore-2024-Getty.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Macklemore-2024-Getty-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Macklemore-2024-Getty-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Macklemore-2024-Getty-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Macklemore-2024-Getty-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 1392px) 100vw, 1392px" /></p><p>由于苏丹持续的危机，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/macklemore">麦克勒莫尔</a>宣布取消即将在迪拜举行的展会，以“抵制在阿联酋做生意”。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/does-rock-n-roll-kill-braincells-macklemore-3402829">摇滚乐会杀死脑细胞吗？！ – 麦克莫尔</a></strong></li></ul><p>在昨天（8 月 24 日）分享的社交媒体帖子中，这位说唱歌手在一份冗长的声明中解释了他的决定。</p><p>今年早些时候，他宣布将于 10 月 4 日在迪拜的可口可乐体育场举行一次性演出。他透露，从那时起，有人联系他，要求他取消约会，“以声援苏丹人民，并抵制在阿联酋做生意，因为他们在该地区持续的种族灭绝和人道主义危机中所扮演的角色， “他写道。</p><p> “对我来说，学习并真正掌握情况很重要。我不想出于恐惧而做出决定，而是发自内心地做出慎重的决定。”</p><p>他详细描述了苏丹的“灾难性”危机，列举了“一千万”流离失所者、“数百万人”面临“迫在眉睫的饥荒”、广泛存在的性暴力以及“至少 15 万人”的死亡人数。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C_Du-kVN09q/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C56