orm.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>这对他来说显然是一个感伤的时刻。 “哦，该死，我很紧张，好吧，”当“Adore U”的第一小节开始演奏时，他说道。 “我想说我完全理解你的感受，因为这是我 16 岁时第一次参加音乐节。我对这件事记得很清楚，”他说。</p><p>随后，他带领观众合唱了一首未发行的歌曲，这首歌是围绕 Nicole Wray 的《Piece Of Me》样本制作的：“<em>我会让你拿走我的一部分/我希望你得到你需要的平静” ，”</em>他唱道。</p><p>整个演出分为三个阶段，见证了他穿越粉丝最喜欢的歌曲，如《丛林》、《克拉拉（夜晚很黑）》和《别管我》。您可以在下面找到完整的歌单。 </p><figure id="attachment_3780195" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3780195" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3780195" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Fred-Again-CREDIT_-Press.jpg" alt="弗莱德又来了.." width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Fred-Again-CREDIT_-Press.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Fred-Again-CREDIT_-Press-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Fred-Again-CREDIT_-Press-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Fred-Again-CREDIT_-Press-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Fred-Again-CREDIT_-Press-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Fred-Again-CREDIT_-Press-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3780195" class="wp-caption-text">再次弗雷德.. – 图片来源：出版社</figcaption></figure><p>在登上舞台之前，弗雷德分享了一段视频，记录了他青少年时期作为赌徒在雷丁大学读书的经历，以及一首新歌采样<a style="font-family: Verdana, BlinkMacSystemFont, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;" href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jamie-t">杰米·T (Jamie T</a> ) 的《Hippodrome》。</p><p>他在 Instagram 的标题中写道：“对我和我们很多人来说，这是我们第一次体验节日。我觉得我们都知道那个节日的感觉是什么！</p><p> “我和朋友们一起浏览了一些照片，我记得有一天晚上结束时，我坐在我们的露营地里，带着温暖的小叮当，听杰米·T。他妈的他真是太棒了。”</p><p>然而，他明确表示这首歌不是<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/fred-again-unveils-details-of-new-album-ten-days-featuring-japanese-house-anderson-paak-sampha-and-more-3780187">他即将于本月早些时候宣布并将于 9 月 6 日发行的专辑《Ten Days》中</a>的歌曲，他写道：“不知道它的用途，因为它听起来一点也不像我的专辑，但听起来就像我现在的感觉如何。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/C_AoFVYom6h/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.899 532.1,66.113 541,66.113 C549.9,66.113 557.115,58.899 557.115,50 C557.115,41.1 549.9,33.886 541,33.886 M565.378,62.101 C565.244,65.022 564.756,66